                    <p>
                        There are two ways to add transactions; adding <a href="@Url.Action("Create","Transactions")"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus-sign"></i></a> them manually
                        or by uploading <a href="@Url.Action("Upload","Transactions")"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-upload"></i></a> an excel file which contains your transactions.
